					"documentation": "# Create Sale Flow of events\n\n## Basic Flow\n\n1. *Seller* inserts the **title**, **description**, **status** and **price**.\n2. *Seller* selects **publication date**.\n3. *Seller* chooses a **file**.\n4. *System* creates a **Sale** with inserted  data and assigns the **Sale** to the **Seller**.\n\n\n## Alternative flow (Sale is not created)\n1. Some fields are empty. System informs the *Seller*.\n2. **price** is not a number. System informs the *Seller*.\n3. **publication date** is before today. System informs the *Seller*.\n4. the **Sale** already exist for this *Seller* (same **title**). System informs the *Seller*.\n",
