				{
					"_type": "UMLUseCase",
					"_id": "AAAAAAGc0jaWAlBKEQw=",
					"_parent": {
						"$ref": "AAAAAAGMFaB678SNc/w="
					},
					"name": "Create Reclamation",
					"ownedElements": [
						{
							"_type": "UMLExtend",
							"_id": "AAAAAAGdNDOaLKA+CfU=",
							"_parent": {
								"$ref": "AAAAAAGc0jaWAlBKEQw="
							},
							"source": {
								"$ref": "AAAAAAGc0jaWAlBKEQw="
							},
							"target": {
								"$ref": "AAAAAAGcmwJ1JS76WFI="
							}
						}
					],
					"documentation": "#CREATE RECLAMATION FLOW OF EVENTS\n\n##BASIC FLOW\n\n1. *Buyer* **show purchaseds** implementaziotik **sale** bat aukeratzen du.\n2. *Buyer* erreklamazio botoia sakatu.\n3. *Buyer* erreklamazioaren zergatia aukeratu/idatzi.\n4. *Buyer* deskripzioa/azalpena idatzi.\n5. *Buyer* erreklamazioa egiteko botoia sakatu.\n6. *Sistemak* **reclamation** bat sortu **status** = irekita izanez, eta datu basean gorde.\n7. *Sistemak* **User**-aren erreklamazioen listan gordetzen du.\n8. *Sistemak* dena ondo joan dela adierazi.\n\n##ALTERNATIVE FLOW\n\n1. Deskripzioa falta.\n2. Zergatia falta."
				},
				{
					"_type": "UMLUseCase",
					"_id": "AAAAAAGc0jdVn3lw+eE=",
					"_parent": {
						"$ref": "AAAAAAGMFaB678SNc/w="
					},
					"name": "Manage Reclamation",
					"ownedElements": [
						{
							"_type": "UMLExtend",
							"_id": "AAAAAAGdND80ljQ1cIU=",
							"_parent": {
								"$ref": "AAAAAAGc0jdVn3lw+eE="
							},
							"source": {
								"$ref": "AAAAAAGc0jdVn3lw+eE="
							},
							"target": {
								"$ref": "AAAAAAGdND4aCxgEhPQ="
							}
						}
					],
					"documentation": "#MANAGE RECLAMATION FLOW OF EVENTS\n\n\n##BASIC FLOW\n\n1. **Admin** **Reclamation** deskripzioa ikusi eta erabaki.\n2. **Admin** **Reclamation** -aren *status* atributua aldatu.\n3. **Admin** bukatzeko sakatu.\n4. **Sistemak** **reclamation**-aren status aldaketa datu basean gorde.\n5. **Sistemak** dena ondo juan dela adierazi.\n\n\n##ALTERNATIVE FLOW\n\n1. **Admin** **Reclamation** -aren *status* aldagaia berdin utzi du."
				},
